<HEADLINE>  INUITS, CANADA REACH ACCORD ON LAND RIGHTS  </HEADLINE>
<MEMO>  Foreign News in Brief  </MEMO>
<TEXT>     With the creation of <LOCATION>Nunavut</LOCATION>, the western half of the <ORGANIZATION>Northwest Territories</ORGANIZATION>
will be renamed.  </TEXT>
