<P>
Photo, Tony Aliengena, right, and Roman Tcheremnykh stand in front of 
Reykjavik's Hofdi House, a government building where Ronald Reagan and Mikhail 
S. Gorbachev met three years ago. Reuters 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
