p.m.</TIME> at <ORGANIZATION>Sterling</ORGANIZATION>'s restaurant, <ORGANIZATION>8737 Fenwick Ave.</ORGANIZATION>, <LOCATION>Sunland</LOCATION>. An admission 
donation of <MONEY>50 cents</MONEY> is requested. 
